Package com.viaoa.jfc.table

Classes that support the table editors for OATable.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
OATableComponent Interface that defines the behavior for OATableComponents to work with an OATable.
OATableListener Implemented by OATable listeners to be able to customize the renderer component for a table cell.
 

Class Summary
OAButtonTableCellEditor Button table editor components.
OACheckBoxTableCellEditor Editor used by OACheckBox when it is used for an OATable column.
OAComboBoxTableCellEditor Used by OAComboBox when used as a column in an OATable.
OAFormattedTextFieldTableCellEditor  
OALabelWithButtonTableCellEditor Label+Button table editor component.
OAPasswordFieldTableCellEditor Password table editor component.
OATableCellEditor Implemented by OATableComponents abstract, must include your own: public abstract Object getCellEditorValue();
OATableCellRenderer Internally used by OATable to wrap a column component and will call the components getTableRenderer() Will also call OATable listeners getTableCellRendererComponent().
OATableColumn Class used to wrap a Table column to work with an OATableComponent.
OATextFieldAutoCompleteListTableCellEditor TextField w/ autocomplete table editor component.
OATextFieldLookupTableCellEditor TextField lookup table editor component.
OATextFieldTableCellEditor TextField table editor component.
OATreeTableCellEditor Tree table editor component.
